  "description": "Figure-8 topology with modDepth pushed to shimmer territory — the pitch modulation on each delay line is offset enough that the reverb tail sparkles rather than wobbles. The feedback loop acts as a spectral multiplier. Input a piano note, output a cathedral made of glass.",
